1
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:23,260
♪Wandering alone♪

2
00:00:23,260 --> 00:00:25,540
♪Walking far by dusk-lit streets♪

3
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:27,430
♪Your eyes are as cold as clouds♪

4
00:00:27,430 --> 00:00:28,970
♪Faintly coming into view♪

5
00:00:28,970 --> 00:00:30,360
♪The city lights♪

6
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:32,630
♪Lit up that single moment♪

7
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:36,140
♪I can't hide or stop missing you♪

8
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:37,640
♪I can't forget those moments♪

9
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,280
♪Losing you♪

10
00:00:39,610 --> 00:00:41,320
♪Like the seasons in my memory♪

11
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:43,290
♪Without winter♪

12
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:44,920
♪Walking down the long, dark street♪

13
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:46,460
♪Snow will never fall again♪

14
00:00:46,460 --> 00:00:48,200
♪Our old story was torn♪

15
00:00:48,200 --> 00:00:50,610
♪Into scattered pieces♪

16
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,430
♪Replaying every single scene♪

17
00:00:53,430 --> 00:00:55,980
♪After you left♪

18
00:00:57,530 --> 00:01:00,510
♪As if our documentary♪

19
00:01:00,510 --> 00:01:03,120
♪Lost winter♪

20
00:01:04,770 --> 00:01:07,180
♪The breeze speaks of good times♪

21
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:11,080
♪Pure white devotion♪

22
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,990
♪Send out a letter♪

23
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:17,780
♪Carrying my longing♪

24
00:01:17,780 --> 00:01:20,980
=The Double Game=

25
00:01:21,020 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 8=

26
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,760
Land reclamation...

27
00:02:14,020 --> 00:02:17,780
(Post)

28
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:23,280
Should I tell Lu Tingxiao
before posting?

29
00:02:26,630 --> 00:02:27,470
Forget it.

30
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:30,310
I did what I was supposed to do.

31
00:02:31,750 --> 00:02:32,590
Why be afraid of him?

32
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:42,150
Tingxiao,

33
00:02:42,470 --> 00:02:43,903
how's it going with the investors

34
00:02:44,190 --> 00:02:45,030
pulling out?

35
00:02:46,710 --> 00:02:47,550
It's settled now.

36
00:02:49,870 --> 00:02:51,400
That was a huge mess.

37
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,520
How did you fix it?

38
00:02:54,870 --> 00:02:56,120
I refunded all their money.

39
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,080
Refunded?

40
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:02,310
Who said you could do that?

41
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,870
I worked so hard to raise that money.

42
00:03:05,190 --> 00:03:06,520
You just refunded it so easily?

43
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:08,520
If it could be refunded,

44
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:09,960
wouldn't I have done it myself?

45
00:03:10,750 --> 00:03:13,240
Do you know how much that was?

46
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:15,630
You've drained

47
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,520
the company's working capital.

48
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,470
If I don't refund it,

49
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:20,840
once this blows up,

50
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:22,310
the company will be done for.

51
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:25,590
Do I need you to teach me business?

52
00:03:26,470 --> 00:03:27,310
This whole thing

53
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,910
shouldn't have been left to you.

54
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:30,470
Jianchuan,

55
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:31,490
look.

56
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,806
Lianxin Island is under seizure.

57
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,080
- What?
- Look.

58
00:03:36,980 --> 00:03:39,560
(Lianxin Island placed under seizure
over illegal reclamation)

59
00:03:45,190 --> 00:03:46,330
- Hey.
- Sis.

60
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:48,080
Did you see the big news alert?

61
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,240
Let me see.

62
00:03:51,305 --> 00:03:53,812
(Lianxin Island placed under seizure
over illegal reclamation)

63
00:03:53,823 --> 00:03:54,663
What?

64
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,080
This isn't right.

65
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:58,680
I just posted the video.

66
00:03:58,840 --> 00:03:59,680
I just hit post.

67
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:01,080
How did it

68
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,800
get officially seized already?

69
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:06,240
Someone must've reported it.

70
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:10,560
What do we do now?

71
00:04:11,420 --> 00:04:14,220
(Jin Chanchan exposes
Lianxin Island reclamation)

72
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:16,430
Jin Chanchan did it.

73
00:04:16,950 --> 00:04:17,920
(Jin Chanchan?)

74
00:04:18,950 --> 00:04:19,790
(Wen Yan?)

75
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,440
Lu Jianchuan,

76
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:22,350
what is going on?

77
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,000
The island was seized!

78
00:04:24,310 --> 00:04:26,120
What did you promise me?

79
00:04:28,750 --> 00:04:29,590
Leave us.

80
00:04:37,072 --> 00:04:38,658
(Chairman of Linhai Group)
It's seized.

81
00:04:38,669 --> 00:04:40,082
(Lin Youqiang)
What about my money?

82
00:04:40,093 --> 00:04:40,933
Will you pay it back?

83
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,240
How much money have I made you?

84
00:04:46,190 --> 00:04:47,030
Without me,

85
00:04:48,390 --> 00:04:50,070
would you be where you are today?

86
00:04:50,270 --> 00:04:51,240
Cut the act with me.

87
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:53,510
You've dragged the development out

88
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,600
for years.

89
00:04:54,870 --> 00:04:56,310
Then let's go

90
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,440
our separate ways.

91
00:04:58,720 --> 00:05:00,190
Is that your plan to keep

92
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,560
the best part?

93
00:05:02,750 --> 00:05:03,590
I'm asking you.

94
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:05,600
Did you bring in Jin Chanchan?

95
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,560
Did you supply the report?

96
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:10,160
Then you leaked some dirt for show.

97
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,430
You think I don't know that?

98
00:05:12,830 --> 00:05:14,560
What Jin Chanchan?

99
00:05:14,776 --> 00:05:15,762
I've never heard of them.

100
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:16,870
Don't make things up

101
00:05:17,070 --> 00:05:18,560
and pin this mess on me.

102
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:22,430
You're not behind it?

103
00:05:23,310 --> 00:05:24,560
Then prove it to me.

104
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:28,200
Jerk.

105
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,190
I'm the scapegoat now?

106
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:31,710
Today,

107
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,830
I'll drag that Jin Chanchan out

108
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,000
and tear them apart.

109
00:05:40,070 --> 00:05:40,910
Lu Jianchuan,

110
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:42,400
don't forget.

111
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,920
Lianxin Island

112
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,360
was mine to begin with.

113
00:05:46,310 --> 00:05:47,150
Don't think

114
00:05:47,510 --> 00:05:49,750
some tourist add-ons and fake papers

115
00:05:49,870 --> 00:05:50,950
make you the boss.

116
00:05:51,430 --> 00:05:52,390
If you push me too far,

117
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:55,270
I'll expose everything.

118
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:57,160
Then we're done for good.

119
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,560
Yan.

120
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,870
Go, now. Go.

121
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,870
Lin Youqiang's inside waiting for you.

122
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:23,350
Go, now!

123
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,680
Don't be scared.

124
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,390
I know his daughter.

125
00:06:26,870 --> 00:06:28,040
He won't do anything to me.

126
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,200
Don't worry.

127
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,760
Yan.

128
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,000
Lin Youqiang.

129
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:05,040
Is violence the only way
you solve things?

130
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:11,680
So, you're Jin Chanchan.

131
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,240
You're the one who's been

132
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,160
spreading lies to smear me.

133
00:07:17,070 --> 00:07:17,910
Lies?

134
00:07:19,190 --> 00:07:20,510
Are they really lies?

135
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,310
All these years on Lianxin Island,

136
00:07:23,950 --> 00:07:26,190
you've conned money, land, and hearts.

137
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:28,360
You even drove people to death.

138
00:07:29,726 --> 00:07:31,033
Do you think trashing this place

139
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:34,310
can cover up what you've done?

140
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:38,680
What proof do you have?

141
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:40,840
Lin Youqiang,

142
00:07:41,010 --> 00:07:41,850
all these years,

143
00:07:41,870 --> 00:07:44,800
you've lived well off blood money.

144
00:07:45,190 --> 00:07:46,950
Haven't you had nightmares?

145
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,510
The people you ruined

146
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,390
are all watching you.

147
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,080
What are you talking about?

148
00:07:54,310 --> 00:07:55,480
I don't get a word of it.

149
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,310
You lied to outsiders

150
00:07:58,270 --> 00:08:00,000
and even to your own family.

151
00:08:00,920 --> 00:08:02,240
Your own child

152
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:04,920
was sent to the Lu family for gain.

153
00:08:06,070 --> 00:08:07,560
You could've been a decent man,

154
00:08:08,270 --> 00:08:10,480
but you chose Lu Jianchuan's pawn.

155
00:08:13,310 --> 00:08:14,150
You...

156
00:08:15,190 --> 00:08:16,040
Who are you?

157
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:19,000
I'm one of the people you ruined.

158
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:31,750
Long time no see.

159
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,200
Dad.

160
00:08:37,870 --> 00:08:39,390
Zhi'er?

161
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,600
So, you're Jin Chanchan.

162
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,320
That's right.

163
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,750
Oh, Jin Chanchan is you.

164
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,360
Then I can relax.

165
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:54,870
Zhi'er,

166
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,480
what you just said was a joke, right?

167
00:08:57,630 --> 00:08:59,080
I wasn't joking with you.

168
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,320
My dear girl.

169
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,480
Hear me out, okay?

170
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,480
I'm not your daughter.

171
00:09:09,030 --> 00:09:10,840
I'm just a tool for your marriage deal.

172
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,510
A puppet that you used

173
00:09:13,030 --> 00:09:15,030
and can be tossed aside anytime.

174
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,480
Do you know how I've lived

175
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:19,630
all these years in the Lu family?

176
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,000
Silly girl.

177
00:09:21,150 --> 00:09:21,990
Yes.

178
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,870
I've failed you all these years.

179
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:26,510
Tell me what I can do to make up for it.

180
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:27,790
I'll agree to anything.

181
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,750
I want you in prison.

182
00:09:40,390 --> 00:09:41,230
Zhi'er,

183
00:09:41,510 --> 00:09:42,790
if I found you today,

184
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:45,790
the Lus can find you tomorrow.

185
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:46,990
Fine.

186
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:48,840
At that time,

187
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,550
I'll stick to one story:

188
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:53,360
You were behind all of this.

189
00:09:54,150 --> 00:09:55,150
Let's see if Lu Jianchuan

190
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:57,120
starts doubting your loyalty.

191
00:09:59,150 --> 00:10:01,200
I really underestimated you.

192
00:10:01,910 --> 00:10:05,030
I didn't expect you to be behind this.

193
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,960
It looks like your alliance is fragile.

194
00:10:10,750 --> 00:10:11,590
You're right.

195
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:12,800
It is fragile.

196
00:10:13,630 --> 00:10:14,470
So,

197
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:15,680
I have to make

198
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,390
some extra preparations.

199
00:10:22,870 --> 00:10:23,710
Chairman Lin.

200
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,280
Tingxiao,

201
00:10:29,583 --> 00:10:30,589
you found this place too.

202
00:10:30,750 --> 00:10:31,590
Perfect timing.

203
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,270
This girl

204
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,750
was actually Jin Chanchan.

205
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:36,480
She's been trying to set us up.

206
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:38,720
This voice recorder is the proof.

207
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,320
Is that so?

208
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:41,920
That's really low.

209
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,480
Then what will you do?

210
00:10:45,150 --> 00:10:47,750
I know right from wrong.

211
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:50,150
Zhi'er is my daughter,

212
00:10:50,510 --> 00:10:52,270
but she's bad for both our families.

213
00:10:52,790 --> 00:10:55,200
So, I'll do what has to be done.

214
00:10:55,870 --> 00:10:56,710
Lin Youqiang,

215
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,480
you're such a beast.

216
00:11:00,390 --> 00:11:01,230
Tingxiao,

217
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,160
you saw it yourself.

218
00:11:02,510 --> 00:11:04,440
This girl still won't change.

219
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,200
Handle this

220
00:11:06,870 --> 00:11:07,710
however you want.

221
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,030
Handle it however I want?

222
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:19,370
Yeah.

223
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:20,630
It's all up to you.

224
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:29,800
This...

225
00:11:46,460 --> 00:11:47,910
♪This door♪

226
00:11:48,310 --> 00:11:53,060
♪Lets in the sky outside♪

227
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:57,100
♪With a voice even lighter♪

228
00:11:57,100 --> 00:11:59,910
♪Than how you just greeted me♪

229
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,730
♪I know now♪

230
00:12:02,060 --> 00:12:06,940
♪What the chill in my body means♪

231
00:12:07,290 --> 00:12:10,160
♪The moment salt hits the wound♪

232
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:13,780
♪My heart still beats so naively♪

233
00:12:13,950 --> 00:12:16,940
♪To complete♪

234
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:21,150
♪A joy that needs no brave pretense♪

235
00:12:21,290 --> 00:12:23,790
♪How cruel sincerity can be♪

236
00:12:23,930 --> 00:12:27,480
♪Like a door with no key♪

237
00:12:27,790 --> 00:12:30,110
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

238
00:12:30,110 --> 00:12:33,690
♪The tears in my eyes♪

239
00:12:34,400 --> 00:12:36,950
♪You looked like you had nothing to say♪

240
00:12:36,950 --> 00:12:38,690
♪Then got so good at being cold♪

241
00:12:38,690 --> 00:12:41,530
♪That's why a smile feels so precious♪

242
00:12:41,740 --> 00:12:43,830
♪Maybe you just passed by♪

243
00:12:43,980 --> 00:12:48,310
♪The tears burned into my heart♪

244
00:12:48,690 --> 00:12:50,980
♪Let's say silence was just for show♪

245
00:12:50,980 --> 00:12:55,650
♪Even if I've grown another year♪
